[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":412},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F30\u002Flearn-hexo-17-next-theme\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F30\u002Flearn-hexo-17-next-theme\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F30\u002Flearn-hexo-17-next-theme\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F30\u002Flearn-hexo-17-next-theme\u002F":389,"related:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F30\u002Flearn-hexo-17-next-theme\u002F":398},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200930\u002F1081826307\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":371,"date":372,"description":19,"extension":373,"lang":374,"meta":375,"navigation":376,"path":377,"readingMinutes":378,"seo":379,"standalone":380,"stem":381,"tags":382,"tldr":386,"updated":372,"url":387,"__hash__":388},"content\u002Fen\u002FHexo\u002Flearn-hexo-17-next-theme.md","(17) Learning Hexo from Scratch - NexT Theme: NexT","7036281801",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":365},"minimark",[11,16,20,24,35,42,61,67,70,73,76,79,83,86,103,114,134,141,147,150,166,169,173,180,187,227,233,247,253,260,332,338,352,358,361],[12,13,15],"h2",{"id":14},"intro","Intro",[17,18,19],"p",{},"This chapter covers NexT, one of the most-used Hexo themes, and one of my personal favourites.",[12,21,23],{"id":22},"what-is-next","What is NexT",[17,25,26,27,34],{},"NexT comes in two flavours. If you search \"Hexo NexT\" on Google you'll probably find the older NexT 5.1.4, with ",[28,29,33],"a",{"href":30,"rel":31},"https:\u002F\u002Ftheme-next.iissnan.com\u002F",[32],"nofollow","this"," as its old site:",[17,36,37],{},[38,39],"img",{"alt":40,"src":41},"Old NexT site","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-30%2013.22.00.png",[17,43,44,45,49,50,54,55,60],{},"The one we'll focus on is NexT v6 and above. The site for this version used to be at ",[28,46,47],{"href":47,"rel":48},"https:\u002F\u002Ftheme-next.org\u002F",[32],", but after the domain expired (if I remember right) it moved to ",[28,51,52],{"href":52,"rel":53},"https:\u002F\u002Ftheme-next.js.org",[32],". The main repo is ",[28,56,59],{"href":57,"rel":58},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fnext-theme\u002Fhexo-theme-next",[32],"here",".",[17,62,63],{},[38,64],{"alt":65,"src":66},"New NexT site","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-30%2013.58.02.png",[17,68,69],{},"So when you download the theme, make sure you grab the right version.",[17,71,72],{},"NexT's popularity comes from a few things: the docs are really clear, the layout is clean, and it integrates a lot of features. The community discussion is huge too — Google \"Hexo NexT tutorial\" and you'll get a flood of hits.",[17,74,75],{},"This series will focus on NexT 7.8.0.",[17,77,78],{},"(While I was writing and editing this post, NexT 8 quietly dropped...)",[12,80,82],{"id":81},"downloading-next","Downloading NexT",[17,84,85],{},"You've installed a couple of themes already by now, so this part should be familiar. But to make sure we're downloading the same thing, here's the command:",[87,88,93],"pre",{"className":89,"code":90,"language":91,"meta":92,"style":92},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","git clone https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Ftheme-next\u002Fhexo-theme-next themes\u002Fnext\n","cmd","",[94,95,96],"code",{"__ignoreMap":92},[97,98,101],"span",{"class":99,"line":100},"line",1,[97,102,90],{},[17,104,105,106,109,110,113],{},"After cloning, update ",[94,107,108],{},"theme"," in ",[94,111,112],{},"hexo\u002F_config.yml",":",[87,115,119],{"className":116,"code":117,"language":118,"meta":92,"style":92},"language-yml shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","theme: next\n","yml",[94,120,121],{"__ignoreMap":92},[97,122,123,126,130],{"class":99,"line":100},[97,124,108],{"class":125},"sKpQp",[97,127,129],{"class":128},"sMAXC",": ",[97,131,133],{"class":132},"sTRMh","next\n",[17,135,136,137,140],{},"Run ",[94,138,139],{},"hexo s"," and you'll see the NexT theme.",[17,142,143],{},[38,144],{"alt":145,"src":146},"Hexo NexT","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-30%2015.39.57.png",[17,148,149],{},"NexT has four built-in styles:",[151,152,153,157,160,163],"ul",{},[154,155,156],"li",{},"Muse",[154,158,159],{},"Mist",[154,161,162],{},"Pisces",[154,164,165],{},"Gemini",[17,167,168],{},"The default style is Muse.",[12,170,172],{"id":171},"next-config","NexT config",[17,174,175,176,179],{},"NexT has a ton of features — ",[94,177,178],{},"theme\u002F_config.yml"," runs over 900 lines. I'll just cover the basics here; we'll get into the details later.",[17,181,182,183,186],{},"Theme switching first. As mentioned, NexT supports four styles. Search for ",[94,184,185],{},"Scheme Settings"," in the config:",[87,188,190],{"className":116,"code":189,"language":118,"meta":92,"style":92},"# Schemes\nscheme: Muse\n#scheme: Mist\n#scheme: Pisces\n#scheme: Gemini\n",[94,191,192,198,209,215,221],{"__ignoreMap":92},[97,193,194],{"class":99,"line":100},[97,195,197],{"class":196},"sQrFR","# Schemes\n",[97,199,201,204,206],{"class":99,"line":200},2,[97,202,203],{"class":125},"scheme",[97,205,129],{"class":128},[97,207,208],{"class":132},"Muse\n",[97,210,212],{"class":99,"line":211},3,[97,213,214],{"class":196},"#scheme: Mist\n",[97,216,218],{"class":99,"line":217},4,[97,219,220],{"class":196},"#scheme: Pisces\n",[97,222,224],{"class":99,"line":223},5,[97,225,226],{"class":196},"#scheme: Gemini\n",[17,228,229,230,232],{},"Comment out ",[94,231,156],{},", uncomment the one you want, restart the dev server, and the style switches.",[17,234,235,236,239,240,243,244,60],{},"Newer NexT also supports dark mode. Search for ",[94,237,238],{},"Dark Mode"," and change ",[94,241,242],{},"darkmode: false"," to ",[94,245,246],{},"darkmode: true",[17,248,249],{},[38,250],{"alt":251,"src":252},"Gemini dark mode","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-31%2021.09.52.png",[17,254,255,256,259],{},"Out of the box, NexT's menu only has home and archives. To add the about page we built earlier, search for ",[94,257,258],{},"Menu Settings"," and uncomment the relevant line:",[87,261,263],{"className":116,"code":262,"language":118,"meta":92,"style":92},"menu:\n  home: \u002F || fa fa-home\n  about: \u002Fabout\u002F || fa fa-user\n  #tags: \u002Ftags\u002F || fa fa-tags\n  #categories: \u002Fcategories\u002F || fa fa-th\n  archives: \u002Farchives\u002F || fa fa-archive\n  #schedule: \u002Fschedule\u002F || fa fa-calendar\n  #sitemap: \u002Fsitemap.xml || fa fa-sitemap\n  #commonweal: \u002F404\u002F || fa fa-heartbeat\n",[94,264,265,273,283,293,298,303,314,320,326],{"__ignoreMap":92},[97,266,267,270],{"class":99,"line":100},[97,268,269],{"class":125},"menu",[97,271,272],{"class":128},":\n",[97,274,275,278,280],{"class":99,"line":200},[97,276,277],{"class":125},"  home",[97,279,129],{"class":128},[97,281,282],{"class":132},"\u002F || fa fa-home\n",[97,284,285,288,290],{"class":99,"line":211},[97,286,287],{"class":125},"  about",[97,289,129],{"class":128},[97,291,292],{"class":132},"\u002Fabout\u002F || fa fa-user\n",[97,294,295],{"class":99,"line":217},[97,296,297],{"class":196},"  #tags: \u002Ftags\u002F || fa fa-tags\n",[97,299,300],{"class":99,"line":223},[97,301,302],{"class":196},"  #categories: \u002Fcategories\u002F || fa fa-th\n",[97,304,306,309,311],{"class":99,"line":305},6,[97,307,308],{"class":125},"  archives",[97,310,129],{"class":128},[97,312,313],{"class":132},"\u002Farchives\u002F || fa fa-archive\n",[97,315,317],{"class":99,"line":316},7,[97,318,319],{"class":196},"  #schedule: \u002Fschedule\u002F || fa fa-calendar\n",[97,321,323],{"class":99,"line":322},8,[97,324,325],{"class":196},"  #sitemap: \u002Fsitemap.xml || fa fa-sitemap\n",[97,327,329],{"class":99,"line":328},9,[97,330,331],{"class":196},"  #commonweal: \u002F404\u002F || fa fa-heartbeat\n",[17,333,334,335,60],{},"By the way, NexT supports fontawesome, so if you want to change a menu icon, just write the fontawesome class after ",[94,336,337],{},"||",[17,339,340,341,344,345,348,349,113],{},"For example, if you want to change ",[94,342,343],{},"about","'s icon to ",[94,346,347],{},"\u003Ci class=\"fas fa-blog\">\u003C\u002Fi>",", write ",[94,350,351],{},"about: \u002Fabout\u002F || fas fa-blog",[17,353,354],{},[38,355],{"alt":356,"src":357},"Was user icon","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-31%2021.15.15.png",[17,359,360],{},"That's it for the first post in the NexT theme chapter.",[362,363,364],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}",{"title":92,"searchDepth":200,"depth":200,"links":366},[367,368,369,370],{"id":14,"depth":200,"text":15},{"id":22,"depth":200,"text":23},{"id":81,"depth":200,"text":82},{"id":171,"depth":200,"text":172},"Hexo","2020-09-30 00:00:01","md","en",{},true,"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002Flearn-hexo-17-next-theme","2",{"title":6,"description":19},false,"en\u002FHexo\u002Flearn-hexo-17-next-theme",[371,383,384,385],"Learning Hexo from Scratch","iThome Ironman 2020","NexT",null,"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F30\u002Flearn-hexo-17-next-theme\u002F","OisaLabQxnf0EpLpfAuHTqFV_-MY9Uind76mxKRZCIs",{"newer":390,"older":394},{"url":391,"title":392,"date":393},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F10\u002F01\u002Flearn-hexo-18-next-structure\u002F","(18) Learning Hexo from Scratch - NexT Theme: Understanding the NexT Structure","2020-10-01 00:00:10",{"url":395,"title":396,"date":397},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F29\u002Flearn-hexo-16-minos-theme\u002F","(16) Learning Hexo from Scratch - Themes: minos","2020-09-29 00:00:02",[399,403,408],{"url":400,"title":401,"date":402,"readingMinutes":378},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2022\u002F10\u002F30\u002Ffix-hexo-updated-date-on-ci-deploy\u002F","Fix: All Posts Show Updated Date After Hexo Upgrade or CI Deploy","2022-10-30 11:52:35",{"url":404,"title":405,"date":406,"readingMinutes":407},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F11\u002F01\u002Flearn-hexo-33-updating-next-theme\u002F","(33) Learning Hexo from Scratch - Extras: Updating the NexT Theme","2020-11-01 13:21:00","3",{"url":409,"title":410,"date":411,"readingMinutes":378},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F10\u002F31\u002Flearn-hexo-32-updating-hexo\u002F","(32) Learning Hexo from Scratch - Extras: Updating Hexo","2020-10-31 14:01:51",1784012773950]